{"type": "article", "id": 10608, "title": "Plant Experiment #1桌面乐高花盆", "description": "", "date": "1970-01-01T00:00:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 1, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235815an2qQOKGpDreoTgS.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t洛杉矶的 <span>NOTCOT </span>公司推出一个三件套的胡桃木植物“花盆”，看起来很像乐高积木，酷炫之处在于这个设计真的是想让你使用乐高，与三个花盆组合到一起，搭建独一无二的桌面迷你世界。有 6×6、8×8、12×12 三种尺寸，非常适合种点多肉植物什么的，底部都有排水设计。每个小方块都是将单独的胡桃木通过数控打磨，最后手工完成的，所以这是每个尺寸只发行 <span>10 </span>个的限量版，售价<span>165 </span>美元（点击这里尝试购买）。<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235812kn9VGHvWcZTBzeAR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235813XZSrjRaIEe3CQYmb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235813EKwM3xiST0fIDbUg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.85333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235813FtGKjHP6myJ5hMYi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.16333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n"}